  "body": "***Type***: Bug\r\n\r\n***Summary***: There is no indication to user that chat name has been edited on chat settings screen: after edit chat name and tap save, - keyboard stays open, save button disappears and user stay on the same screen thinking that nothing happened, but chat name has been changed under the hood. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nNo cursor with keyboard upon tap 'Save' button on 'Chat settings' screen when editing chat name\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nCursor in chat name and keyboard keep stay upon tap 'Save' button on 'Chat settings' screen when editing chat name\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Create group chat with Jarrad\r\n- From group chat screen tap top-right group chat icon -> Settings\r\n- Esit group chat name\r\n- Tap 'Save' button\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\nStatus version: Develop (9f9155, 0.9.11d629), Release 0.9.13\r\nOperating System: Android 7.0, Android 6.0, iOS (11.2.2)\r\n\r\nTF session: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/7636860/sessions/2/?accessToken=ixdHYVEoPWO--CN7ck6lixx7ri4",
